text:
It's really bustling!
So many people are here...
Ah, everyone looks like they're enjoying the food.

It must be a dish
truly beloved by the locals.

I was curious,
so I came to eat with Producer.

Since you're here, please eat a lot before you leave!
It's on the house!

No, no...!
It's more enjoyable to buy these things myself...!

(This kindness, valuing connections with others,
is part of Juri's charm...)
